    <title>MRepoApp/MRepo</title>
    <updated>2024-02-18T01:50:03Z</updated>
    <id>tag:github.com,2024-02-18:/MRepoApp/MRepo</id>
    <link href="https://github.com/MRepoApp/MRepo" rel="alternate"></link>
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;A Modules Manager for Magisk &amp; KernelSU&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h1&gt;MRepo&lt;/h1&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/releases&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/MRepoApp/MRepo?label=release&amp;amp;color=red&#34; alt=&#34;release&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/releases/latest&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://shields.io/github/downloads/MRepoApp/MRepo/total?label=download&#34; alt=&#34;download&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.me/mrepo_news&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/badge/Telegram-blue.svg?label=follow&#34; alt=&#34;follow&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://weblate.sanmer.app/engage/mrepo/&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://weblate.sanmer.app/widgets/mrepo/-/svg-badge.svg?sanitize=true&#34; alt=&#34;translated&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;MRepo (short for &lt;code&gt;My Repository&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;Modules Repository&lt;/code&gt;) is an Android app that helps manage your own modules repository.&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Preview&lt;/h2&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/main/fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/1.png&#34; width=&#34;32%&#34;&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/main/fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/2.png&#34; width=&#34;32%&#34;&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/main/fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/3.png&#34; width=&#34;32%&#34;&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/main/fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/4.png&#34; width=&#34;32%&#34;&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/main/fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/5.png&#34; width=&#34;32%&#34;&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MRepoApp/MRepo/main/fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/images/phoneScreenshots/6.png&#34; width=&#34;32%&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Supported Versions&lt;/h2&gt; &#xA;&lt;ul&gt; &#xA; &lt;li&gt;Android 8.0 ~ 14&lt;/li&gt; &#xA; &lt;li&gt;Magisk 24.0 ~ latest&lt;/li&gt; &#xA; &lt;li&gt;KernelSU 0.5.1 ~ latest&lt;/li&gt; &#xA;&lt;/ul&gt; &#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Modules Repository&lt;/h2&gt; &#xA;&lt;ul&gt; &#xA; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MRepoApp/magisk-modules-repo-util&#34;&gt;magisk-modules-repo-util&lt;/a&gt;: the util to help build modules repository&lt;/li&gt; &#xA; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MRepoApp/magisk-modules-alt-repo&#34;&gt;MRepoApp/magisk-modules-alt-repo&lt;/a&gt;: a mirror of Magisk-Modules-Alt-Repo&lt;/li&gt; &#xA;&lt;/ul&gt; &#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Credits&lt;/h2&gt; &#xA;&lt;ul&gt; &#xA; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/tabler/tabler-icons.git&#34;&gt;tabler/tabler-icons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</summary>
  </entry>
